TASK: Generate {{ count | default(5) }} multiple-choice quiz questions about the following topic.
TOPIC: {{ topic }}
DIFFICULTY: {{ difficulty | default("medium") }}
Difficulty guide - easy: recall and recognition; medium: understanding and application; hard: analysis and synthesis.
Respond ONLY with valid JSON: { "questions": [ { "id": 1, "question": "Question text?", "options": ["Option A", "Option B", "Option C", "Option D"], "correct_index": 0, "explanation": "Why this answer is correct." } ] }
Rules:
- Return one JSON object only.
- Do not wrap the JSON in markdown fences.
- Do not include commentary before or after the JSON.
- Each question must have exactly 4 options.
- correct_index is 0-based.
- All options must be plausible.
- No trick questions.
- Distribute correct answers across all indices.
